Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on object detection in real-world scenes using deep learning techniques. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel anchor-offset detection mechanism and dual refinement networks for accurate object detection, which involves AI techniques. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses deep learning techniques for object detection. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper applies the proposed methods to underwater object grasping with an autonomous system. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with object detection in images and videos, which are multimedia data.
